.description
A ready-to-link SAS-objectfile with a nice ScreenModeRequester.  Features
include programmable property-lists, font-sensitivity,
screensize-sensitivity and autocenter.  Easy to use and pretty.  For WB2.0+
Public Domain software.  Includes the object, headerfile, C-example and
autodocs.  Source available from author.  Tested with WB2.0 WB3.1.  
